{"_id":"cNPGemSftteSCdBN","name":"Memory of the Dragon","type":"gift","img":"icons/creatures/eyes/lizard-single-slit-pink.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer","scenarioSlug":"saint-george-the-dragon-slayer","sourceDirectory":"saint-george-the-dragon-slayer","contentKey":"scenario-gift.saint-george-the-dragon-slayer.memory-of-the-dragon","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":1,"folderName":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer"}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p>You have discovered the truth about Saint George's past—that his friendship with the Dragon was real, that the plague was orchestrated, and that the entire tragedy was manipulated by the One Who Plots in the Shadows. This terrible knowledge has awakened something within you: the memory of the Dragon's perspective. Once per Session, you can spend 2 Soma to access the Dragon's ancient wisdom. For the rest of the Scene, you gain the Descriptor **'I remember what the Dragon knew about ancient laws and betrayals.'** This grants you knowledge about: the true nature of binding oaths and ancient laws, how to recognize manipulation by the One Who Plots, the history of conflict between humans and magical creatures, and ways to resist corruption. Additionally, while this Descriptor is active, Saint George (if present) will become visibly shaken when you speak with the Dragon's wisdom, reducing his Opposition Level by 1 as his resolve wavers with painful memories.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Saint George the Dragon Slayer","somaCost":2,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer","source":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.saint-george-the-dragon-slayer.memory-of-the-dragon","scenario":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer","scenarioSlug":"saint-george-the-dragon-slayer","sourceDirectory":"saint-george-the-dragon-slayer","tags":[],"requirements":"","limitations":""},"sort":1300000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332113,"modifiedTime":1784280332113,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"Comdqj1RdAh0lHHg","name":"Paladin's Oath","type":"gift","img":"icons/magic/holy/chalice-glowing-gold-water.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer","scenarioSlug":"saint-george-the-dragon-slayer","sourceDirectory":"saint-george-the-dragon-slayer","contentKey":"scenario-gift.saint-george-the-dragon-slayer.paladin-s-oath","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":2,"folderName":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer"}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p>You have earned the respect of one of Saint George's Paladins through your actions, and they have shared with you the sacred oath that binds them to their cause. Choose one of the six Paladins you encountered. You gain insight into their special ability and can invoke their spirit once per Scene to aid you. **Trebizond** (create exotic equipment Descriptor, +1 OL when using it), **Demetrius** (take 1 Wound for ally, +1 OL rest of Scene), **Theodore** (inflict 1 Additional Wound when raging, or 1 Wound even on successful Defense), **Martha** (enemies get 2 Penalties when targeting you if other allies present), **Syrus** (negate one Hunter Gift effect per Scene), or **Margaret** (gain +1 OL for each Wound Saint George has suffered). You can only invoke the chosen Paladin's power once per Scene, and it lasts for a single action. The Paladin you choose reflects your own values and fighting style.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Saint George the Dragon Slayer","somaCost":1,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer","source":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.saint-george-the-dragon-slayer.paladin-s-oath","scenario":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer","scenarioSlug":"saint-george-the-dragon-slayer","sourceDirectory":"saint-george-the-dragon-slayer","tags":[],"requirements":"","limitations":""},"sort":1400000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332114,"modifiedTime":1784280332114,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
{"_id":"3T3AQy5hzxrlzKT4","name":"The Saint's Blessing","type":"gift","img":"icons/magic/holy/angel-winged-humanoid-blue.webp","effects":[],"folder":null,"flags":{"broken-tales":{"category":"scenario-gift","scenario":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer","scenarioSlug":"saint-george-the-dragon-slayer","sourceDirectory":"saint-george-the-dragon-slayer","contentKey":"scenario-gift.saint-george-the-dragon-slayer.the-saint-s-blessing","role":"scenario-gift","sequence":3,"folderName":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer"}},"system":{"description":"<h3>Scenario Gift</h3><p>Saint George has recognized your good intentions and blessed you with a fragment of his holy power. Once per Scene, when you would suffer a Wound from a creature with monstrous, magical, or supernatural Descriptors, you can invoke the Saint's protection to reduce the damage. Roll 1 die: on a result of 4-6, you completely avoid the Wound; on 1-3, you still suffer it but gain 1 Additional Success on your next action against that creature. Additionally, you get 1 Additional Success on all Defense Checks against attacks from Dark Presences who serve the One Who Plots in the Shadows, as Saint George's blessing reveals their true nature.</p>","notes":"Scenario Gift - Saint George the Dragon Slayer","somaCost":0,"automaticSuccesses":0,"owner":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer","source":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer","category":"scenario-gift","key":"scenario-gift.saint-george-the-dragon-slayer.the-saint-s-blessing","scenario":"Saint George the Dragon Slayer","scenarioSlug":"saint-george-the-dragon-slayer","sourceDirectory":"saint-george-the-dragon-slayer","tags":[],"requirements":"","limitations":""},"sort":1500000,"ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"coreVersion":"14.365","systemId":"broken-tales","systemVersion":"0.2.17","createdTime":1784280332114,"modifiedTime":1784280332114,"lastModifiedBy":null,"exportSource":null}}
